snippet.title: We Harvest Shadows - Official Developer Overview Trailer | Indie Horror Showcase 2024
snippet.description:
Join the developer of We Harvest Shadows for a deeper look into the world, vehicles, and nightmares coming to the first-person farming horror allegory game. Become a recluse, build up your farm, and survive the lonely nights. We Harvest Shadows will be available on PC, and a demo is out now on Steam.

#IGN #Gaming
